act.article:
2 In these rules 


a    the Act means the Industrial Disputes 
  Act, 1947 (14 of 1947); 

b    Chairman means the Chairman of the 
  Tribunal; 

c    member means a member of the 
  Tribunal; 

d    section means a section of the Act; 


e    Tribunal means the Industrial 
  Tribunal constituted under section 7 consisting of two or more members.
